
---
const SITE_TITLE = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_SITE_TITLE ?? 'EcoVision';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>{SITE_TITLE}</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 800px; margin:auto; padding:40px;">
  <h1>{SITE_TITLE}</h1>

  <p>
    EcoVision is a community-driven platform for reporting environmental hazards 
    like waste dumping, polluted water, and unsafe drainage.
  </p>

  <h2>Report a Hazard</h2>
  <p>
    <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfoVrPjZdw6ex2LiDTUwLs1E2z1LVMVYEeJUrt_RfgFdV4cYw/viewform?usp=dialog" 
       target="_blank" 
       style="background:#28a745;color:white;padding:10px 20px;text-decoration:none;border-radius:5px;">
      Click here to submit a report
    </a>
  </p>

  <h2>About EcoVision</h2>
  <p>
    Join our community to help monitor environmental hazards in your area. Your reports help us track issues and take action.
  </p>

  <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
  <p>
    EcoVision is a community-driven platform. We do not verify or guarantee the accuracy of user submissions.
    Submitted data is used solely for environmental monitoring purposes. EcoVision does not guarantee any response or action.
    Users are responsible for their own safety when reporting hazards.
  </p>
</body>
</html>